<article id="article" class="article "><header><h1 class="title" itemprop="headline">60 Minutes investigates hidden motors and pro cycling</h1>

					<p class="dek">Bill Whitaker investigates whether pro cyclists have used secret bike motors to win races -- like the Tour de France -- in a sport notorious for its culture of cheating</p>
		
    </header><div class="social sharebar_expanded inline-sharebar theme-light  location-top" data-component="sharebar">

